ily-militias-gangs-brazil/" data-reactid="370"><div class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-thumbnail" data-reactid="371"><img height="440" src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/a4d611cd-eb98-4904-ae76-9c37f9b6d340/a4d611cd-eb98-4904-ae76-9c37f9b6d340.bin?auto=compress,format&amp;cs=srgb&amp;dpr=2&amp;h=440&amp;w=440&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces%2Cedges&amp;_=5d2f26172bf9a1db3ec33f4ce4610adc" width="440" data-reactid="372"/></div><h4 class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-title" data-reactid="373">Video: As Brazil’s Jair Bolsonaro Prepares to Meet Donald Trump, His Family’s Close Ties to Notorious Paramilitary Gangs Draw Scrutiny and Outrage</h4></a></div></div><!-- react-empty: 374 --><div class="SeriesBlock SeriesBlock--end" data-reactid="375"><div class="SeriesExcerpt" data-reactid="376"><h2 class="SeriesExcerpt-title" data-reactid="377"><a class="" href="/series/secret-brazil-archive/" data-reactid="378"><span class="SeriesTitle" data-reactid="379"><span class="SeriesTitle-title" data-reactid="380">Secret Brazil Archive</span></span></a></h2><div class="SeriesExcerpt-description" data-reactid="381"><p class="Excerpt" data-reactid="382">A massive trove of previously undisclosed materials provides unprecedented insight into the operations of the anti-corruption task force that transformed Brazilian politics and gained worldwide attention.
</p></div></div><span class="Expandable Expandable--collapsed" data-reactid="383"><button class="Expandable-button" data-reactid="384"><span data-reactid="385"><span class="Icon Icon--Arrow_01_Down icon-TI_Arrow_01_Down" data-reactid="386"></span><!-- react-text: 387 --> <!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 388 -->Expand All Parts<!-- /react-text --></span></button><div class="Expandable-content" data-reactid="389"><div class="Expandable-content-wrapper" data-reactid="390"><div class="SeriesBlock-social" data-reactid="391"><span class="SeriesBlock-social-label" data-reactid="392">Share the whole series</span><div class="Series-social" data-reactid="393"><div class="Series-social-wrapper" data-reactid="394"><div class="Series-social-item Series-social-facebook" data-reactid="395"><a class="Series-social-link" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheintercept.com%2Fseries%2Fsecret-brazil-archive%2F" style="background:transparent;color:;" data-reactid="396"><span class="Icon Icon--Facebook icon-TI_Facebook" data-reactid="397"></span></a></div><div class="Series-social-item Series-social-twitter" data-reactid="398"><a class="Series-social-link" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Secret%20Brazil%20Archive%20%E2%80%94%20an%20investigative%20series%20by%20%40theintercept%20https%3A%2F%2Ftheintercept.com%2Fseries%2Fsecret-brazil-archive%2F" style="background:transparent;color:;" target="_blank" data-reactid="399"><span class="Icon Icon--Twitter icon-TI_Twitter" data-reactid="400"></span></a></div><div class="Series-social-item Series-social-mail" data-reactid="401"><a class="Series-social-link" href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#" style="background:transparent;color:;" data-reactid="402"><span class="Icon Icon--Envelope icon-TI_Envelope" data-reactid="403"></span></a></div></div></div></div><!-- react-empty: 404 --></div></div></span></div><div class="Post-latest-articles" data-reactid="405"><h4 class="Post-latest-articles-header" data-reactid="406">Latest Stories</h4><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="407"><div data-reactid="408"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="409"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/18/trump-latin-america-foreign-policy-joe-biden/" data-reactid="410"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="411"><div class="Promo-image-container" data-reactid="412"><div class="Promo-image-block" data-reactid="413"><div class="ResponsiveImage Promo-image" style="padding-top:50%;" data-reactid="414"><noscript data-reactid="415"><img src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/68115254-b698-4c8d-93e3-ae18f013e128/68115254-b698-4c8d-93e3-ae18f013e128.bin?auto=compress,format&cs=srgb&dpr=2&h=450&w=900&fit=crop&crop=faces%2Cedges&_=96d69908306e5168585e8e7a6f71fecb" alt="null" class="ResponsiveImage-image" height="900" width="1800"></noscript></div></div></div><div class="Promo-text" data-reactid="416"><div class="PromoVideoPlayButton Promo-playButton Promo-playButton--in-title" data-reactid="417"></div><div class="Promo-title-block" data-reactid="418"><h4 class="Promo-title" data-reactid="419"><span class="Promo-title-wrap" data-reactid="420">We Need to Reverse the Damage Trump Has Done in Latin America. Biden’s Plans Don’t Cut It.</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="421"><!-- react-text: 422 -->John Washington<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="423"><!-- react-text: 424 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 425 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="426">Apr. 18</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-excerpt" data-reactid="427"><!-- react-empty: 428 --></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="429"><div data-reactid="430"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="431"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/18/trump-urges-followers-risk-lives-rallies-wont-attend/" data-reactid="432"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="433"><div class="Promo-image-container