rtainly.%20The%20problem%20is%2C%20will%20the%20father%20let%20him%3F%20Or%20worse%2C%20if%20the%20father%20is%20implicated%2C%20what%20does%20this%20thing%20with%20the%20loans%20indicate%3F%3C%2Fh6%3E%0A%3Ch6%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22color%3A%20%23000000%22%3EDallagnol%20%E2%80%93%2008%3A54%3A21%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20any%20case%2C%20the%20president%20will%20not%20split%20from%20his%20son.%20And%20what%20if%20all%20this%20happens%20before%20the%20vacancy%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20appears%3F%3C%2Fh6%3E%0A%3Ch6%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22color%3A%20%23000000%22%3EDallagnol%20%E2%80%93%2009%3A04%3A38%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20During%20interviews%2C%20they%20will%20certainly%20ask%20about%20this.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20any%20way%20to%20avoid%20the%20question%2C%20but%20I%20can%20go%20to%20different%20depths.%201%29%20this%20is%20something%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated%3B%202%29%20everything%20indicates%20this%20is%20one%20of%20those%20salary%20kickback%20schemes%2C%20like%20the%20one%20involving%20Aline%20Correa%20that%20we%20prosecuted%2C%20or%2C%20even%20worse%2C%20phantom%20employees.%3C%2Fh6%3E%0A%3Ch6%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22color%3A%20%23000000%22%3EDallagnol%20%E2%80%93%2009%3A05%3A54%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Now%2C%20to%20what%20extent%20will%20%5Bthe%20president%5D%20really%20fight%20for%20Moro%E2%80%99s%20anti-corruption%20agenda%20if%20his%C2%A0%20son%20is%20in%20the%20firing%20line%3F%3C%2Fh6%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%3C%21--%20BLOCK%28photo%29%5B4%5D%28%257B%257D%29%28%257B%2522scroll%2522%253Afalse%252C%2522align%2522%253A%2522center%2522%252C%2522width%2522%253A%2522px%2522%257D%29%20--%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22img-wrap%20align-center%20%20width-fixed%22%20style%3D%22width%3A%20px%3B%22%3E%3C%21--%20CONTENT%28photo%29%5B4%5D%20--%3E%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheintercept.com%2Fwp-uploads%2Fsites%2F1%2F2019%2F06%2Fst8-1560024775.png%22%3E%3Cimg%20class%3D%22alignright%20size-thumbnail%20wp-image-253919%22%20src%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheintercept.com%2Fwp-uploads%2Fsites%2F1%2F2019%2F06%2Fst8-1560024775.png%22%20alt%3D%22%22%20%2F%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%21--%20END-CONTENT%28photo%29%5B4%5D%20--%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%21--%20END-BLOCK%28photo%29%5B4%5D%20--%3E%3Cbr%20%2F%3E%0A\">\u003c!-- CONTENT(section)[2] --\>\u003cbr />\n\u003c!-- BLOCK(photo)[3](%7B%7D)(%7B%22scroll%22%3Afalse%2C%22align%22%3A%22center%22%2C%22width%22%3A%22px%22%7D) --\>\u003cdiv class=\"img-wrap align-center  width-fixed\" style=\"width: px;\">\u003c!-- CONTENT(photo)[3] --\>\n\u003cimg class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-253917\" src=\"https://theintercept.com/wp-uploads/sites/1/2019/06/st7-1560024676.png\" alt=\"\" />\n\u003c!-- END-CONTENT(photo)[3] --\>\u003c/div>\u003c!-- END-BLOCK(photo)[3] --\>\u003c/p>\n\u003ch6>\u003cstrong>\u003cspan style=\"color: #000000\">December 8, 2018 – Telegram group &#8220;Filhos do Januario 3&#8243;\u003c/span>\u003c/strong>\u003c/h6>\n\u003cp>&nbsp;\u003c/p>\n\u003ch6>\u003cstrong>\u003cspan style=\"color: #000000\">Deltan Dallagnol – 00:56:50 –\u003c/span>\u003c/strong>  \u003ca href=\"https://noticias.uol.com.br/politica/ultimas-noticias/2018/12/07/bolsonaro-diz-que-ex-assessor-tinha-divida-com-ele-e-pagou-a-primeira-dama.htm\">https://noticias.uol.com.br/politica/ultimas-noticias/2018/12/07/bolsonaro-diz-que-ex-assessor-tinha-divida-com-ele-e-pagou-a-primeira-dama.htm\u003c/a>\u003c/h6>\n\u003ch6>\u003cstrong>\u003cspan style=\"color: #000000\">Dallagnol – 00:58:15 –\u003c/span>\u003c/strong> [image not found]\u003c/h6>\n\u003ch6>\u003cstrong>\u003cspan style=\"color: #000000\">Dallagnol – 00:58:15 –\u003c/span>\u003c/strong> [image not found]\u003c/h6>\n\u003ch6>\u003cstrong>\u003cspan style=\"color: #000000\">Dallagnol – 00:58:38 –\u003c/span>\u003c/strong> COAF [money-monitoring agency] under Moro\u003c/h6>\n\u003ch6>\u003cstrong>\u003cspan style=\"color: #000000\">Dallagnol – 00:58:40 –\u003c/span>\u003c/stron